    • Method Detail

      • getConstructors

        public Constructor[] getConstructors()
        Returns an array of the public constructors of the class represented by this node. The returned array may be shared with other callers. It must not be modified.
        Returns:
        an array of the class constructors

      • getEnumNames

        public String[] getEnumNames()
        If the class represented by this node is an enumeration, returns the names of the enumeration values. If the class is not an enumeration, returns an empty array.
        Returns:
        the members of this enumeration, or an empty array

      • getFields

        public Field[] getFields()
        Returns an array of the public fields of the class represented by this node. The returned array may be shared with other callers. It must not be modified.
        Returns:
        an array of static fields

      • getJavaClass

        public Class getJavaClass()
        Returns the Java Class object for the class represented by this class node.

        Do not confuse this with getClass(), which will return the class object for the ClassNode class itself.

        Returns:
        the class object for the class represented by this node
        Throws:
        ClassNotFoundException - if no class exists for this node

      • getMethods

        public Method[] getMethods()
        Returns an array of the public, non-static methods of the class represented by this node. The returned array may be shared with other callers. It must not be modified.
        Returns:
        an array of the class constructors

      • getParameterNames

        public String[] getParameterNames(AccessibleObject m)
        This method returns parameter names for the parameters of one of the methods or constructors of the class represented by this node. If the compiled class is available, and was compiled with debugging information, the actual parameter names will be returned. Otherwise, parameter names will be generated based on the parameter types. The returned array may be shared with other callers. It must not be modified.
        Parameters:
        m - the method or constructor to return parameter names for
        Returns:
        an array of parameter names

      • getStaticFields

        public Field[] getStaticFields()
        Returns an array of the public, static fields of the class represented by this node. The returned array may be shared with other callers. It must not be modified.
        Returns:
        an array of static fields

      • getStaticMethods

        public Method[] getStaticMethods()
        Returns an array of the public, static methods of the class represented by this node. The returned array may be shared with other callers. It must not be modified.
        Returns:
        an array of the class constructors
